title: Wall Street supports Bush, Clinton for sake of stability
text:
Wall Street supports Bush, Clinton fo... Wall Street supports Bush, Clinton for sake of stability There are 2 comments on the Reuters story from 15 hrs ago, titled Wall Street supports Bush, Clinton for sake of stability . In it, Reuters reports that: 
Wall Street employees are donating to Bush and Clinton's presidential campaigns as they seek stability and predictability says Larry Sabato. Of the nearly twenty presidential candidates out there new data shows that to have garnered clear support from Wall Street Jeb Bush and Hillary Clinton.
